<summary>
The <strong><c>repeat()</c></strong> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</see> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Functions">function</see> represents a repeated fragment of the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_grid_layout/Basic_concepts_of_grid_layout">track list</see>, allowing a large number of columns or rows that exhibit a recurring pattern to be written in a more compact form.
</summary>
<remarks>
